&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;At Navan, the &lt;strong&gt;Associate Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; (AAE) is the strategic partner to our &lt;strong&gt;Senior Account Executives&lt;/strong&gt; on 6 and 7-figure deals. This is an elite “sales school&quot; designed for ambitious professionals, who are ready to move away from transactional cycles and into the world of complex, multi-stakeholder corporate software sales.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why This Role?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;This is a 15 month runway. We aren&#39;t looking for someone to stay an Associate forever; we are hiring the next generation of Sales Talent. If you have the ability to think strategically, the&amp;nbsp; fluency in German to dominate the DACH market, as well as being resilient and driven, we want to talk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &quot;Navan MBA&quot; - What You’ll Master&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;We don’t just expect you to know the playbook; we teach it to you. You will exit this role with the expertise in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The MEDDPICC Framework&lt;/strong&gt;: You’ll learn to break down complex deals into actionable step using the gold standard of corporate sales methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Navigation: &lt;/strong&gt;How to move past gatekeepers to build genuine partnerships with C-suite stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Enterprise Playbook:&lt;/strong&gt; From initial discovery to the final &quot;Closed-Won&quot; step, you’ll see exactly how the world’s biggest deals are won.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Account Mapping: &lt;/strong&gt;You aren&#39;t just &quot;prospecting.&quot; You’re conducting deep-dive research into org charts to identify pain points and map Navan’s value proposition to their bottom line.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deal Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Senior AEs to conduct targeted outreach to C-Suite stakeholders. You aren&#39;t just setting meetings; you’re co-driving the business case.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intelligence Gathering:&lt;/strong&gt; Map out the &quot;political landscape&quot; of prospect organizations. Who is the Economic Buyer? Who is the Champion? You’ll find out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A &quot;Strategic&quot; Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; we are looking for initial full-time experience in Consulting, M&amp;amp;A, Private Equity, Strategy.&amp;nbsp;You know how to ask the second and third layer of questions to find the real problem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Language Mastery: &lt;/strong&gt;C2 fluency in German and at least B2 in English. You can navigate a complex business negotiation in both languages with ease.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unrivaled Drive:&lt;/strong&gt; You are a self-starter who doesn&#39;t wait for a manual. You have a &quot;founder&quot; mentality — if a process is broken, you fix it; if a door is closed, you find a window.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Thinking:&lt;/strong&gt; You can look at a global corporation and logically deduce which stakeholders need to be involved and what their unique incentives are.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Presence: &lt;/strong&gt;You are comfortable and articulate when speaking with VPs and C-Suite executives. You trade in value, not just features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

