&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Language&lt;/strong&gt;: Fluency in English and French - Mandatory fluency in both languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Service&lt;/strong&gt;: Background in contact center or customer-facing roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tech Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Comfortable using tools like Gmail, Zendesk, Slack, and Salesforce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Availability&lt;/strong&gt;: Flexible to work rotating shifts, Monday to Sunday, between 7 AM and 11 PM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills&lt;/strong&gt;: Ability to multitask, resolve urgent matters quickly, and work independently to troubleshoot issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attitude&lt;/strong&gt;: Empathetic, professional, and excellent at communicating verbally and in writing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

